      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS BEAR (8) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at her last three on end, the latest at this track (29.85). Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. BENTLEY KRISTOFF (7) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 6 length win at this track in a handy 29.61. Wide box to overcome but likes the trip. One of main contenders. SMOKY CHIPOTLE (1) recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 6 length second behind BENTLEY KRISTOFF in 30.02. Expecting another bold showing. COUNTRY FORM (3) is a chance after winning last time.",
